ASoC: soc-core: Merge CPU/Codec for soc_dai_pcm_new()

Now CPU/Codec DAIs are alias for dais.
Thus, we can directly use for_each_rtd_dais() macro
for soc_dai_pcm_new().
This patch merge CPU/Codec for it.

